data.description: Welcome to Dove Crossing! Located in the new heart of McAllen, Texas, this meticulously built home boasts at 2,134 square feet of living space and 3,103 square feet of total space. It comes fully equipped with 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, 2-door garage, dining room, kitchen, breakfast nook, spacious living room, foyer, and laundry room, with ceilings ranging from 9 to 10 feet tall in all areas. This home includes a water softener, custom shutters on all windows, outdoor shed, irrigation system, and a spacious back porch and yard. The master bedroom speaks for itself upon entering it. Garage located in the rear of the house that has access to an alley. The lot is approximately .19 acres and zoned in the Edinburg Independent School District. Enjoy the prime location this home lies within, with easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, airports, colleges and universities, South Padre Island, Mexico, and more!
